Hey this is easy guys;
you deploy an app in IaaS meaning you are consuming IaaS services (SCENARIO). So the features (how will IaaS behave) of IaaS will apply in that, what is the CSP responsible for and what you as a consumer is responsible for.
(SOLUTION)IaaS will only be responsible for the remote datacenter, hosting your infrastructure and the physical networking to ensure seamless flow of data in the datacenter, also including real-time monitoring to ensure no faults in the servers, storage facilities and their networking.
Your obligation is manage your OS, Network controls (firewalls,VPNs), your App, device, accounts and identities accessing your app, Identity provider and most importantly your information and data.
You still don't see the answers? 
for Business analytics I can say it's a SaaS (software that helps you analyze your data and find possible ways you can use the analytics to get new ideas advancing=from my point of view )
